item.content:encoded:
Jamil Jahangir – ReZero.
“ReZero” is a single released by Jamil Jahangir. It was Initially released as a demo in December 2020 on SoundCloud.
ReZero is influenced by the OST from the futuristic video game “Cyberpunk” and the movie “Tenet”. The theme of ReZero is being chased in a futuristic dystopian world.
